title: ‘You’ Season 4: Ed Speleers Talks About Joining The Serial Killer Drama
description: “I’ve played some fairly contentious individuals, but this felt like something that was going into a new world, and with the cult following, I had to do it,” said Ed Speleers of joining the fourth season of the Netflix hit 'You.'
keywords: Ed Speleers, Joe Goldberg, Rhys Montrose, Outlander, British

title: Roku Could Swing to a Loss on Weak Ad Spend, Despite Account Growth
description: Roku reports Q4 results after markets close on Feb. 15. Inflation could weaken ad revenue, leading to a loss, despite strong accounts growth.
